The '''1983 World Junior Ice Hockey Championships''' (''1983 WJHC'') was the 7th edition of the [[World Junior Ice Hockey Championships]] and was held in [[Leningrad]], [[Soviet Union]] between [[December 26]], [[1982]] and [[January 4]], [[1983]].  The host [[Soviet Union national ice hockey team|Soviet team]] won the tournament with a perfect 7<U+2013>0 record.

==Tournament results==
The tournament was a round-robin format, with each team playing each of the other seven teams once each.
